2005 • 1h 27m
Family, Comedy, Fantasy, Musical

Description
Handsome hero Prince Dauntless is desperate to find a wife, but just when he thinks he's found "the one," his mother cooks up a test that is sure to get rid of her…or so she thinks.
Click to expand...
More Information
Long Description:
Queen Aggravain sabotages the efforts of every young princess who hopes to marry her son, Prince Dauntless—and decrees no one else can wed until he does. But since Honorable Sir Harry is determined to marry the lovely Lady Larken, he sets off for faraway lands to find a match for the Prince. He returns with an unlikely candidate: Princess Winnifred from the swamps. It’s love at first sight for the Prince, but the Queen isn't convinced and cooks up a "sensitivity" test. The palace is filled with merriment and mischief while everyone wonders: Will Princess “Fred” pass the Queen’s test?
